    {
      "id": "detailed_3_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_3",
      "description": "This vehicle is in truly mint condition, appearing and driving as if it just rolled off the showroom floor. The exterior paint is flawless with a deep shine, and the interior is pristine, showing no signs of wear or age. Mechanically, it is perfect, with a whisper-quiet engine and seamless performance that reflects its meticulous care. This is a rare find for a buyer seeking a vehicle in showroom-quality condition with absolutely no compromises.",
