    },
    {
      "id": "detailed_2_listing_0",
      "firm_id": "detailed_2",
      "description": "This vehicle is in fair condition and serves as a dependable daily driver, though it does show clear signs of its age and mileage. The exterior has various minor scratches, some noticeable paint fading on the hood and roof, and a small ding on the rear passenger door. Inside, the upholstery is intact but shows some staining and general wear from regular use. Mechanically, the car runs well and has been regularly maintained, though it may soon require routine service for wear-and-tear items like brake pads or tires. It is a solid, honest car for someone who prioritizes functionality and reliability over a flawless appearance.",
      "price": 18500.0,
