      "description": "Presenting a distinguished vehicle that exemplifies mechanical integrity and sustained performance. This unit has been curated for the driver who demands a balance of reliability and sophisticated engineering. Having undergone a comprehensive professional assessment, the vehicle demonstrates consistent power delivery and a well-preserved interior environment. While exhibiting the honest character of a seasoned motorcar, its structural and functional components remain robust, ensuring a refined driving experience. This is an exceptional opportunity to acquire a high-caliber vehicle that maintains a commanding presence on the road.",
      "price": 29900.0,
